Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.01,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:43.30,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無法忘懷的喜歡的地點
