Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:50.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}讓失去生氣的氣球重新飄起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.03,0:23:57.76,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}lalala  Goodbye  昨日的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:05.08,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}在今天到來之時長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:11.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}就像那天看到的花火一樣
